metadata.name: Horrible Sanity
metadata.description:
I BECAME INSANE WITH LONG INTERVALS OF HORRIBLE SANITY.

This photo was shot on foggy morning with temperature touching almost 3 C. I used an RGB Light app in my mobile to get an Alien look and tried to blend it with the yellow color of flowers.

Fun Fact: The field was having water from the last day. So it was little difficult to get in. But to get the desired composition my brother sacrificed his shoes.

Artist : Adnan_Dani  
Edition : 1\1  
Specifications : 2472 x 3090
